            },
            {
              "blockId": "840aad43-1d2b-a6a0-92ef-97e3026c9e0d",
              "type": "altText",
              "model": {
                "blocks": [
                  {
                    "blockId": "3298d981-5b5a-1fcf-c615-7a14e799349a",
                    "type": "text",
                    "model": {
                      "text": "Galileo"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "blockId": "d6a2db75-b1f7-5c52-8080-5dbeefd1e7a8",
              "type": "caption",
              "model": {
                "blocks": [
                  {
                    "blockId": "e9c95639-8b60-0e2a-de2f-e41ad6eda538",
                    "type": "text",
                    "model": {
                      "text": "The Galileo system was conceived to give Europe an independent sat-nav capability"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "blockId": "304bdd68-b564-441a-b127-dc30fea49781",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "fd41138e-02a1-503c-c486-9c0e3af6de2b",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": "David Davis's Brexit department will also warn the scheme could cost the EU an extra €1bn (£876m) without the UK's continued involvement. "
              }
            },
            {
              "blockId": "ed255587-67fd-9167-6400-53d88a97ab94",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": " "
              }
            },
            {
              "blockId": "8b4bc2bf-7a40-1014-8b81-607e3ea08147",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": " The row could harm wider post-Brexit security co-operation, it will say in a paper to be published later."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "blockId": "97d3f8d8-be5c-4aed-a87c-5afa472a5e09",
        "type": "headline",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "03576ee9-e45a-7df7-23ee-9bcb1470b92b",
              "type": "text",
              "model": {
                "text": "Brexit: UK to demand EU pays back £1bn in Galileo costs"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "blockId": "9f4f70af-112f-4002-a880-d56a69427826",
        "type": "subheading",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "263f94fb-a68d-0909-f780-f987c87e6dfd",
              "type": "text",
              "model": {
                "text": "The UK wants the EU to repay £1bn if it is excluded from the Galileo satellite navigation system after Brexit."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "blockId": "0bfeebf6-6a93-470a-95e6-9f51b39208a1",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "f517acb4-5ae1-885c-aced-16bd0beea07e",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": "UK ministers are angry about the EU's decision to limit access to Galileo, an alternative to the US GPS system."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "blockId": "65372fd8-0261-4553-8ff2-35858a0370fe",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "5c368460-2878-8022-9025-87d0c29835c7",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": "The UK played a major role in developing satellites for Galileo, which is expected to be fully operational in 2026."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "blockId": "ba6c6ecc-9c08-4db8-a4a1-838d61abcad3",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "6793b736-190a-8cd5-59fb-017056765e78",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": "But Brussels has cited legal issues about sharing sensitive information with a non-member state for its decision to shut British firms out of the project. "
              }
            },
            {
              "blockId": "881a059b-d56f-e4c2-f15b-1209de291f6e",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": " Brussels has also said it will restrict access to encrypted signals from Galileo, prompting the UK government to threaten to build its own satellite navigation system."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "blockId": "583f3e6e-2663-45c6-bb4a-eadb997e8e6d",
        "type": "subheading",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "cee81fa9-eaa3-ee29-3e25-a99c7c0fcefe",
              "type": "text",
              "model": {
                "text": "It will not be straightforward to effectively fulfil all Galileo security work elsewhere"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "blockId": "2e51abfa-81b6-4de5-9b43-b73864323076",
        "type": "subheading",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "2062dd5d-dc0e-f8cb-3d86-1a7c7e84204f",
              "type": "text",
              "model": {
                "text": "Brexit customs plan 'could cost £20bn"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "blockId": "1d449d81-030c-45f7-a008-cd19e9b1b777",
        "model": {
          "blocks": [
            {
              "blockId": "df25ce53-fd62-f698-62fc-a3d78619f5cd",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "model": {
                "text": "The UK government has also threatened to block Galileo satellites from using ground tracking stations in British overseas territories such as the Falklands.[UK ups the ante on _Galileo project_](http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-44116085).The European Commission says the UK will have to apply to use the Public Regulated Service (PRS), a key element of the Galileo system, like any other non-EU country after its March 2019 departure."
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}